<div class="mode-context">
    <header class="mode-context-header">
        <a href="settings-import.html" class="mode-context-back button button-link">
            <svg class="iconic">
                <use xlink:href="../../img/material/svg-sprite-navigation-symbol.svg#ic_arrow_back_24px"></use>
            </svg>
            <span class="hidden">Back</span>
        </a>

        <h1 class="mode-context-title">Import CSV</h1>
    </header>
</div>

<main role="main">

    <div class="full-col">

        <div class="form-sheet">
            <div class="form-sheet-summary">
                <h2 class="form-sheet-title"><em>filename.csv</em> is being imported</h2>
                <progress max="100" value="60">
                    <div class="progress-bar">
                        <span style="width: 60%;">Progress: 60%</span>
                    </div>
                </progress>

                <!--progress>
                    <div class="progress-bar">
                        <span style="width: 100%;"></span>
                    </div>
                </progress-->

                <p>The data from your CSV spreadsheet is still being processed. You're welcome to leave or wait until the process is complete. Either way, we'll notify you when your data is ready.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="form-sheet-actions">
                <div class="form-field">
                    <a href="settings.html" class="button">Return to settings</a>
                    <a class="button button-gamma button-flat" data-toggle="csv_import">Import another CSV file</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-sheet">
            <div class="form-sheet-summary">
                <h2 class="form-sheet-title"><em>filename.csv</em> was successfully imported</h2>
                <p>The data from your CSV spreadsheet was successfully imported into your <a href="">Street Maintenance</a> survey.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="form-sheet-actions">
                <div class="form-field">
                    <a class="button button-alpha">See imported data</a>
                    <a class="button button-gamma button-flat" data-toggle="csv_import">Import another CSV file</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-sheet">
            <div class="form-sheet-summary">
                <h2 class="form-sheet-title">We ran into some problems importing <em>filename.csv</em></h2>
                <p><strong>88 records</strong> from your CSV spreadsheet were sucessfully imported. But the rest couldn't be imported because <em>reasons</em>.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Reason 1</li>
                    <li>Reason 2</li>
                    <li>Reason 3</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We'd suggest fixing these issues in your CSV file and trying to import the file again.<p>
            </div>

            <fieldset>
                <legend>What do you want to do with the 88 records that were successfully imported?</legend>

                <div class="form-field radio">
                    <label for="keep_records-false">
                        Remove them. I'll re-import them when I revise my CSV file.
                        <input type="radio" checked id="keep_records-false" name="keep_records" />
                    </label>
                </div>

                <div class="form-field radio">
                    <label for="keep_records-true">
                        Keep them. I won't include them in my revised CVS file.
                        <input type="radio" id="keep_records-true" name="keep_records" data-fieldgroup-toggle="view-records" />
                    </label>
                </div>
            </fieldset>

            <div class="form-sheet-actions">
                <div class="form-field">
                    <a class="button" data-toggle="csv_import">Import revised CSV file</a>
                    <span data-fieldgroup-target="view-records">
                        <a class="button button-gamma button-flat">View 88 imported records</a>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {{> CSVimport hidden='true'}}

    </div>

</main>

<div id="import-complete" class="message">
    <div class="message-body">
        <p><strong>Your CSV import</strong> is complete.</p>
        <p>The data from your CSV spreadsheet, <em>filename.csv</em>, was successfully imported into your <a href="">Street Maintenance</a> survey.</p>

        <button class="button-alpha">See imported data</button>
        <button class="button-flat message-trigger">Dismiss</button>
    </div>
</div>

